milestones.description: John Mooney and Paul Stirling's 76-run partnership is IRE's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 73 between Kevin O'Brien and Alex Cusack

stories.title: Stirling, McCallan set up Ireland whitewash
stories.subTitle: Ireland v Kenya, 3rd ODI, Dublin
stories.summary: Over the past two years, Ireland have replaced Kenya as the best Associate, and again today in the third ODI at Clontarf, the home side proved their worth with a tense four-run win
